ace="Verdana">The purpose of this study was to determine the    prevalence of se
rum cobalamin deficiency among Costa Rican young adults and    to examine whethe
r dietary intake of vitamin B<SUB>12 </SUB>and the presence    of <I>H. pylori <
/I>help to explain serum vitamin B<SUB>12</SUB> concentrations.</font></p>     ^
