ace="Verdana">Written, informed consent was obtained from all    participants. T
he study protocol was approved by the Ethics Committees of the    Costa Rican In
stitute for Research and Education on Nutrition and Health (INCIENSA)    and the
 University of Costa Rica.</font></p>     ^cY#a05v22n6.htm##
